SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: BRAD GREER IS THE IIABA NATIONAL DIRECTOR AND SERVES ON THE EXECUTIVE COMMITTEE. HEATH GREER IS BRAD'S SON AND SERVES ON THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS. BOTH WORK AT THE SAME AGENCY.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Section A, Line 4
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: DURING THE FISCAL YEAR, THE ORGANIZATION CHANGED ITS PROCESS FOR TERMINATION, EXPULSION, OR SUSPENSION OF MEMBERS; CHANGED DUTIES OF NOMINATING COMMITTEES TO BE DUTIES OF THE EXECUTIVE COMMITTEE; AND ALLOWED THE OPTION FOR THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS TO VOTE TO ALLOW AN INDIVIDUAL TO SERVE MORE THAN TWO CONSECUTIVE TERMS.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: Form 990, Part VI, Section A, Line 6
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: The membership of this Association shall be composed of: (1) Regular Members; (2) Associate members; and (3) Retired members.
